title: Enabling integrated bone growth with 3D printed metal implants
text:
Enabling integrated bone growth with 3D printed metal implants 1 October 2015 Expand Metal additive manufacturing company, Arcam , talk to TCT about their electron beam melting technology, which is perfect for 3D printed medical implants. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
